  "instructions": [
    "Air-fry the baby aubergines at 375°F for about 8 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "In a bowl, mix together olive oil, salt, garlic cloves, red pepper flakes, cumin powder, turmeric powder, coriander (ground), and lemon juice. Add pomegranate syrup and stir well.",
    "Drain the air-fried baby aubergines on paper towels to remove excess oil, then toss them in the seasoning mixture until coated evenly.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds over the seasoned aubergine for extra texture and flavor."
